metadata.yaml\n121:   - Purpose: Verify fallback to third filename when first two missing\n122:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:106-118`\n123:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_fallback_metadata_yaml -v`\n124: \n125: - [x] **T4.8**: Test load_metadata FileNotFoundError when all missing\n126:   - Purpose: Verify FileNotFoundError raised when no metadata files exist\n127:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:158-160`\n128:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_no_files -v`\n129: \n130: - [x] **T4.9**: Test save_metadata YAML format\n131:   - Purpose: Verify YAML dumped with default_flow_style=False, indent=2, sort_keys=False\n132:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:120-141`\n133:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_save -v`\n134: \n135: - [x] **T4.10**: Test save_metadata excludes None values\n136:   - Purpose: Verify model_dump(exclude_none=True) behavior\n137:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:143-156`\n138:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_save_excludes_none -v`\n139: \n140: - [ ] **T4.11**: Test update_metadata partial field update\n141:   - Purpose: Verify update_metadata applies partial updates correctly\n142:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py`\n143:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_update -v`\n144: \n145: - [ ] **T4.12**: Test update_metadata returns updated AgentMetadata\n146:   - Purpose: Verify update_metadata returns new AgentMetadata instance\n147:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py`\n148:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_se