ts |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Modified | 8 | Export providers |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### KubernetesProvider Key Features\n\n- **NodePort Service**: Creates NodePort type Service for external access\n- **Deployment Management**: Creates/patches Deployments with env vars and entrypoint\n- **Readiness Waiting**: Polls deployment status with configurable timeout\n- **Error Handling**: Handles 409 (conflict) by patching, ignores 404 on delete\n\n### AgentCubeProvider Key Features\n\n- **Custom Resource**: Uses CustomObjectsApi for AgentRuntime CR\n- **CRD Constants**: Defines group, version, plural for AgentRuntime CRD\n- **Readiness Probe**: Configures HTTP readiness probe with defaults\n- **ImagePullSecrets**: Sets default-secret for image registry auth\n\n### Provider Selection Pattern\n\n```python\nif provider == \"k8s\":\n    from agentcube.services.k8s_provider import KubernetesProvider\n    self._k8s_provider = KubernetesProvider(verbose=verbose)\nelif provider == \"agentcube\":\n    from agentcube.services.agentcube_provider import AgentCubeProvider\n    self._agentcube_provider = AgentCubeProvider(verbose=verbose)\nelse:\n    raise ValueError(f\"Invalid provider: {provider}. Must be 'agentcube' or 'k8s'\")\n```\n\n### AgentRuntime Endpoint Rewrite\n\nFor AgentRuntime CR invocations, the endpoint URL is rewritten:\n```\nOriginal: http://api-server.example.com\nRewritten: http://api-server.example.com/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{name}/invocations/\n```\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| Phase 1: KubernetesProvider | T1.1-T1.11 | Done | 100% |\n| Phase 2: AgentCubeProvider | T2.1-T2.7 | Done | 100% |\n| Phase 3: K8s Tests | T3.1-T3.23 | Done | 100% |\n| Phase 4: AgentCube Tests | T4.1-T4.20 | Done | 100% |\n| Phase 5: Runtime Integration | T5.1-T5.8 | Done | 100% |\n| Phase 6: Runtime Tests | T6.1-T6.21 | Done | 100% |\n| Phase